<%# ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<div class="onboarding-hero">
  <div class="container py-5 text-center text-white">
    <%= image_tag "marc", alt: "Marc Thomas", class: "onboarding-avatar mb-4", style: "width: 130px; height: 130px;" %>
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-1">Marc Thomas</h1>
    <p class="lead onboarding-hero-sub mb-0">Développeur Web Full-Stack junior</p>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ── BIO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-intro-card p-4 p-md-5">
    <p class="fs-5 lh-lg mb-0">
      Après plusieurs années dans le conseil en financement de projets innovants et l'accompagnement
      stratégique d'entreprises, j'ai choisi de me réorienter vers le développement web afin de contribuer
      directement à la création de solutions technologiques. Mon expérience en innovation et gestion de
      projet me permet de comprendre les enjeux business et de faire le lien entre équipes techniques et
      décideurs.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ── EXPÉRIENCE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<section class="bg-white py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="onboarding-section-bar"></span>
      <h2 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Expérience</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Consultant en financement de projet</h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">EPSA &middot; CDI &middot; Lyon, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes</p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">mars 2022 – sept. 2025</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Customer Success Manager</h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Agicap &middot; Lyon, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes</p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">oct. – déc. 2021</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Bras droit CEO</h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Gilbert Paris &middot; Stage &middot; Paris, Île-de-France</p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">févr. – août 2021</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Stagiaire chargé d'études sectorielles</h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Groupe Xerfi &middot; Stage &middot; Lyon</p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">juin – sept. 2020</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ── FORMATION ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<section class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="onboarding-section-bar"></span>
      <h2 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Formation</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Le Wagon</h5>
            <p class="mb-1 text-muted">Concepteur &amp; développeur d'application web &middot; RNCP niveau 6</p>
            <p class="mb-0 small text-muted">
              Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, HTML/CSS, SQL/PostgreSQL, APIs REST, Git, Agile, IA
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">janv. – mars 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm onboarding-step-card p-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Université Lumière Lyon 2</h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Master Management de l'Innovation et Propriété Intellectuelle (MIPI)</p>
          </div>
          <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge align-self-start">2019 – 2021</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ── COMPÉTENCES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<section class="bg-white py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="onboarding-section-bar"></span>
      <h2 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Compétences</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Ruby on Rails</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">JavaScript</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">HTML / CSS</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">PostgreSQL</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">APIs REST</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Git / GitHub</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Agile</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Gestion de l'innovation</span>
      <span class="badge onboarding-role-badge fs-6 px-3 py-2">Gestion de projet</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ── RETOUR ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container py-4 text-center">
  <%= link_to "← Retour à l'onboarding", onboarding_path, class: "btn onboarding-team-btn fw-bold" %>
</div>
